r this service?","a":"Enter Austriany; register address; apply for residence permit at Ausländerbehörde within visa validity."},{"q":"Is Admission from recognised Austrian institution required?","a":"Admission from recognised Austrian institution is typically required."},{"q":"Is admission documentation (India) required?","a":"Apply early—processing takes weeks"},{"q":"Is Proof of funds or financial proof required?","a":"required living funds for 2026 or equivalent"},{"q":"Is Health insurance (travel + statutory) required?","a":"Assess whether Health insurance (travel + statutory) is satisfied for this case."},{"q":"Is Motivation letter and CV required?","a":"Motivation letter and CV is typically required."},{"q":"Is Language proficiency (as required) required?","a":"Austrian or English per program"},{"q":"Is Valid passport required?","a":"Valid passport is typically required."},{"q":"What is the Processing time?","a":"6–12w — After complete file + APS"},{"q":"What is the Government fee?","a":"€75 — + proof of funds required living funds"},{"q":"What is the Our approval rate?","a":"88% — ~74% benchmark"},{"q":"What is the Required docs?","a":"15 — + APS & proof of funds"},{"q":"What is the Consultancy fee?","a":"See fee tab — + govt & third-party"},{"q":"What if the client has APS not completed?","a":"Complete APS before embassy slot; track processing on APS website"},{"q":"Why is APS not completed a problem?","a":"Visa appointment booked without admission documentation."},{"q":"What if the client has Insufficient proof of funds?","a":"Open proof of funds at approved bank for full required amount"},{"q":"Why is Insufficient proof of funds a problem?","a":"Amount below required monthly sum or not from recognised provider."}]'::jsonb
